#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "thag16.5:4.1"
msgid ""
"<span class=\"var\" title=\"māluṅkyaputtatheragāthā (bj)\" id=\"note373\">"
"16.5 Mālukyaputtattheragāthā</span>"
msgstr "16.5. Māluṅkyaputta"

#. </h1></div><blockquote class="gatha"><p><a class="sc" id="1"></a><a
#. class="verse-num-sc" id="verse-num-sc794"></a><a class="verse-num-pts"
#. id="verse-num-pts794"></a>
msgctxt "thag16.5:5.1"
msgid ""
"<span class=\"cross\" title=\"^sn35.95#1 [95. Mālukyaputtasutta]\" id=\""
"note374\">*</span>“Rūpaṃ disvā sati muṭṭhā,"
msgstr "When you see a sight, mindfulness is lost"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.5:5.2"
msgid ""
"<span class=\"var\" title=\"piya (s2, s3, pts1)\" id=\"note375\">Piyaṃ</span>"
" nimittaṃ manasi karoto;"
msgstr "as attention latches on the pleasant aspect."

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.5:5.3"
msgid "Sārattacitto vedeti,"
msgstr "Experiencing it with a mind full of desire,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.5:5.4"
msgid "Tañca ajjhosa tiṭṭhati."
msgstr "you keep clinging to it."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="2"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc795"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts795"></a>
msgctxt "thag16.5:6.1"
msgid "Tassa vaḍḍhanti vedanā,"
msgstr "Many feelings grow"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.5:6.2"
msgid "anekā rūpasambhavā;"
msgstr "arising from sights."

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.5:6.3"
msgid "Abhijjhā ca vihesā ca,"
msgstr "The mind is damaged"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.5:6.4"
msgid "cittamassūpahaññati;"
msgstr "by covetousness and cruelty."

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.5:6.5"
msgid "Evamācinato dukkhaṃ,"
msgstr "Heaping up suffering like this,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag16.5:6.6"
msgid ""
"ārā <span class=\"var\" title=\"nibbānaṃ (bj)\" id=\"note376\">nibbāna</span>"
" vuccati."
msgstr "you’re said to be far from quenching."

